16356   
16357     Delay_process : PROCESS (clk)
16358     BEGIN
16359       IF clk'EVENT AND clk = '1' THEN
16360         IF reset_x = '1' THEN
16361           Delay_out <= (OTHERS => '0');
16362         ELSIF enb = '1' THEN
16363           Delay_out <= parity_out;
16364         END IF;
16365       END IF;
16366     END PROCESS Delay_process;
16367   
16368   
16369   
16370     Delay_out1 <= Delay_Initial_Val_out WHEN Delay_ctrl_delay_out = '0' ELSE
16371         Delay_out;
16372   
16373     Logical_Operator_out1 <= serial_out XOR Delay1_out1;
16374   
16375     Delay1_process : PROCESS (clk)
16376     BEGIN
16377       IF clk'EVENT AND clk = '1' THEN
16378         IF reset_x = '1' THEN
16379           Delay1_out1 <= '0';
16380         ELSIF enb = '1' THEN
16381           Delay1_out1 <= Logical_Operator_out1;
16382         END IF;
16383       END IF;
16384     END PROCESS Delay1_process;
16385   
16386   
16387     ce_out <= clk_enable;
16388   
16389     out_rsvd <= Delay1_out1;
16390   
16391   END rtl;
